                            <comment id="13533598" author="cheolsoo" created="Mon, 17 Dec 2012 01:30:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached is a patch that does the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Convert Cluster and PigServer to ThreadLocal&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Randomize the destination of input file in the cluster so that input files don&apos;t conflict when multiple jobs run in parallel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
